    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709665110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=426\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709665110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1075\" data-width=\"1915\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612401259\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392822785\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"871ce8bf-b03f-4938-8ea7-600963e2cdd0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709665110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=852 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758709665110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=426 1x\"></span><p>If you are using a UVd model and have already painted the maps in Mari or Substance Painter, then you should be all set.</p><p>In RenderMan, manifolds tell the renderer how to apply patterns on a surface, and several nodes control the placement and repetition of textures, but the main one we’re going to look at first is the PxrManifold2D.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Pxrmanifold2d.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705630440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=212\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705630440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"268\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612171938\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Pxrmanifold2d.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392822785\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"97448edb-6e42-40d2-ba43-22ba6cff1761\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705630440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=268 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705630440&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=212 1x\"></span><p>Its primary job is to control the tiling, transformation, and randomization of textures and can be connected to a PxrTexture node, as seen in the example below.  Once set up, you will now be able to repeat the tiling, rotate and transform the texture, and apply random offsets/rotations to multiple pieces of geometry.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Pxrmanifold2d_2.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705721162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=212\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705721162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"268\" data-width=\"960\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612171945\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Pxrmanifold2d_2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392822785\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"51f43266-5193-46d1-833a-075046af8912\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705721162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=960&amp;height=268 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705721162&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=212 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Pxrmanifold2d_3.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705875921&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=438\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705875921&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"785\" data-width=\"1362\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612171952\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Pxrmanifold2d_3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392822785\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"ba09d8c9-ee23-4782-9bb4-93daf6836bf0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705875921&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1362&amp;height=785 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758705875921&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=438 1x\"></span><p>As mentioned above, several other texture manifolds ship with RenderMan, and we’ll cover each one in other lessons.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Pxrmanifold2d_4.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758706289656&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=438\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758706289656&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"785\" data-width=\"1362\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"612401239\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Pxrmanifold2d_4.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"392822785\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"9b4768c1-706c-4ed2-9721-5da58ce08bba\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758706289656&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1362&amp;height=785 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/392822785/Pxrmanifold2d_4.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758706289656&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=438 1x\"></span><hr/><h3 id=\"ControllingTextures-Manifolds\">Manifolds</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224071\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrManifold2D</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542222866\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrBumpManifold2D</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224088\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrManifold3D</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224403\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrProjector</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224582\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrRandomTextureManifold</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224705\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrRoundCube</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225110\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrTileManifold</u></a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542223991\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>PxrHexTileManifold</u></a></p></li></ul><p />"
    }
